title.narrative: Enhancing Nigeria's Response to HIV/AIDS - Procurement of Goods

description.narrative: This activity (Enhancing Nigeria's Response to HIV/AIDS - Procurement of Goods) is a component of Enhancing Nigeria's Response to HIV/AIDS reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of goods' and a budget of £43,310,356. This component benefits Nigeria, and works in the following sector(s): Family planning, STD control including HIV/AIDS. , with the following implementing partners: Crown Agents Limited, Oxford Policy Management. The start date is 04-02-2009 and the end date is 31-12-2016.
